title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_1
tags:
---
Rojul: The sun’s just peeking over the ridge.
Rojul: Looks like it’s shy today.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_2
tags:
---
Rojul: That golden light never gets old.
Rojul: It's like the sky is pouring honey.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_3
tags:
---
Rojul: I watched the shadows retreat this morning.
Rojul: They don't fight the light. They just make way.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_4
tags:
---
Rojul: Sunrise always makes the metal on my hands glow.
Rojul: Like I’m holding something sacred.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_5
tags:
---
Rojul: I used to run on power cells.
Rojul: Now? I think I run on sunlight.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_6
tags:
---
Rojul: The sky’s painting again.
Rojul: Reds, oranges… all for no one in particular.
===


title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_7
tags:
---
Rojul: The grass glows at this hour.
Rojul: Like it's been saving its color just for the sun.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_8
tags:
---
Rojul: I stood still as the sun rose.
Rojul: For a moment, I forgot I was built. I just was.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_9
tags:
---
Rojul: The cold fades fast once the sun climbs.
Rojul: Like it’s pulling warmth back into the world.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_10
tags:
---
Rojul: The world looks softer at sunrise.
Rojul: Like it hasn't decided what kind of day to be yet.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_11
tags:
---
Rojul: A fresh shadow means a fresh day.
Rojul: And I've still got oil in the joints. Let’s go.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_12
tags:
---
Rojul: If you listen real close, you can hear the light arriving.
Rojul: It hums gently. Like hope.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_13
tags:
---
Rojul: The sunrise caught on the water trough.
Rojul: For a second, it looked like fire.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_14
tags:
---
Rojul: Funny how the sunrise always feels new.
Rojul: Even after a thousand of 'em.
===

title: background_dialogue_rojul_sunrise_15
tags:
---
Rojul: The light moves slow over the plain.
Rojul: Like it knows this is a place to take your time.
===
